{"tid":1859784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲係天真期望政府回應？","createTime":"2020-02-03T10:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T10:37:58.000Z","uid":269642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6eca86452f1e043c1252d81b179e0d99ea91eaa","tid":1859784,"uid":269642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"先幫大家重溫一下記憶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FVm0PR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FVm0PR.jpg&h=3bab4c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗而家⋯<br />\n仲咁天真認為港共政權會聽市民意見？<br />\n仲諗住可以退落嚟忍下就算？<br />\n仲認為呢一刻手握公權力一方會放過香港人？<br />\n仲覺得呢個政權會回應訴求？<br />\n⋯<br />\n根本唔可能！<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不是民選的政府<br />\n是不會回應訴求的<br />\n香港需要的是革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"}]}